{"tid":1587653,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【覺悟撚】點解要繼續生存？","createTime":"2019-09-22T13:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T03:07:42.000Z","uid":125976,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fb3bd88e5e28fb42b716793077b95e4c84c9d710","tid":1587653,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:22:57.000Z","msg":"𠵱個世界<br />\n<br />\n有人出世就生於富貴之家，並且天資聰敏，有優良嘅資源同環境栽培，將來出社會就出人頭地，名成利就<br />\n<br />\n有人出世就生於貧賤之家，並且天資平庸，加上得劣質嘅教育資源同環境下成長，將來只注定做出生富貴之家嗰啲人隻狗<br />\n<br />\n又有人天生性格樂天外向、運動型、高大樣靚身型正，即使花心亦屌女無數<br />\n<br />\n又有人天生性格消極內向、毒宅型、矮細樣衰又太肥，即使對異性尊一真心亦不斷收好人卡，注定 A0 或不斷被傷害<br />\n<br />\n咁天生喺𠵱條不公平線下嘅人，理性嚟睇仲應唔應該繼續痛苦咁生存落去？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78faf5a1e8bc1c23a5624b43e7e0e7823f4c0ae","tid":1587653,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c937bc608d7d4685a5e05952b1474fb95b55b553","tid":1587653,"uid":247184,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:24:33.000Z","msg":"因為上世唔知做錯咩，所以要今世受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fc2155e20b35d74ef1355911f3b839d1cce99d","tid":1587653,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"5a73437d4c6907c381caa793fd4c02a85835e5ea","tid":1587653,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:17:00.000Z","msg":"so u jump LOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651293a570ef4bd6a216ffcce90fa1676dd151a3","tid":1587653,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-